{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDQ3NzAyMTU2", "number": 5813, "title": "feat: organize UDFs by category", "bodyText": "A little friday afternoon, quality-of-life-improvement: i noticed that we now have quite some UDFs, which is cool, but the list you get when executing show functions is quite long and hard to navigate unless you really know what you are looking for. Hence this PR adds a new categorization of UDFs into STRING|AGGREGATE|ARRAY|... etc.\nAlso a small message at the end of the listing detailing how to get further information about a function of interest.\nLooks like quite a lot of changes but most of it is just inserting the appropriate category into the source file of each individual UDF.", "createdAt": "2020-07-11T01:44:44Z", "url": "https://github.com/confluentinc/ksql/pull/5813", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "7f5b843c628248b21e8796d71fecd1242f29c497"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-07-14T23:11:26Z", "author": {"login": "blueedgenick"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 16, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABc0mD8vgFqTQ0NzUxMjgyNA==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABc09b-1gH2gAyNDQ3NzAyMTU2OjcxOGU5Mzc4NTFmZWExNzQyYThmODg4NzgxZDUyOGUxNjAyODIwMzY=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NDQ3NTEyODI0", "url": "https://github.com/confluentinc/ksql/pull/5813#pullrequestreview-447512824", "createdAt": "2020-07-13T18:50:51Z", "commit": {"oid": "aa21d2aa0d1d45d33a587b9ff43b1932a229ce41"}, "state": "COMMENTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 1, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wNy0xM1QxODo1MDo1MVrOGw1bNQ==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wNy0xM1QxODo1MDo1MVrOGw1bNQ==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ1Mzg2MDE0OQ==", "bodyText": "Suggested change\n        \n          \n    \n\n        \n      \n    \n    \n      